sources.description:
Don't open the door! The night he came to town, the terror began!
Random people are terrorized by a malevolent man wearing a black leather glove with razor-fingers, who brings their worst fears to life.

Original title: The Demon (1979) Also known as: Midnight Caller / The Unholy

Director & Writer:  Percival Rubens
Main Cast:
Jennifer Holmes as Mary
Cameron Mitchell as Col. Bill Carson
Craig Gardner as Dean Turner
Zoli Marki as Jo


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles)
01:32 A missing girl sparks a series of terrifying events, as psychic powers reveal a demonic presence stalking the town.
26:34 Characters revisit haunting memories and realize they are in greater danger than they imagined.
52:45 Chilling events escalate in a house, as eerie encounters and dark predictions foreshadow horror to come.
1:08:53 A terrifying presence closes in on Mary, Bobby, and Jo as fear and paranoia reach a breaking point.
